<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Halaman Utama</title>
    <style>
        /* Gaya CSS internal untuk tampilan yang lebih menarik */
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #a8c0ff, #3f2b96);
            background-size: 400% 400%;
            animation: gradient-animation 15s ease infinite;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        /* Animasi untuk gradien */
        @keyframes gradient-animation {
            0% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
            50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
            100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
        }

        .container {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            padding: 40px 60px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 500px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease-in-out;
        }
        
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        h1 {
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 2.8em;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
        }
        
        p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        
        .link-container {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        
        a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #fff;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #007bff, #0056b3);
            padding: 16px 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.3);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        a:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px) scale(1.02);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.4);
            color: #fff;
        }

        /* Efek hover glossy */
        a::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: -100%;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            transition: all 0.4s ease;
        }
        
        a:hover::after {
            left: 100%;
        }

        .secondary-link {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #6c757d, #5a6268);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(108, 117, 125, 0.3);
        }
        
        .secondary-link:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(108, 117, 125, 0.4);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>ðŸ‘‹ Selamat Datang!</h1>
        <p>Ayo mulai kelola tugas-tugas Anda dengan mudah.</p>
        <div class="link-container">
            <a href="/todos-list">Lihat Daftar Tugas</a>
            <a href="/contact" class="secondary-link">Hubungi Kami</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>